OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK debt interest payments  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhit record high in February
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rising inflation led to government     
OL,6, interest payments hitting a fresh      
OL,7, record in February, official data show.
OL,9,FInterest payments reached #8.2bn last  
OL,10,Fmonth, the highest amount for a        
OL,11,FFebruary since records began in April  
OL,12,F1997 and up #1bn on last year.         
OL,14,FThe payments are pegged to the Retail  
OL,15,FPrices Index (RPI) measure of inflation
OL,16,F- which reached 7.8% in January.       
OL,18,FIt comes as pressure mounts on the     
OL,19,FChancellor Rishi Sunak to take action  
OL,20,Fto tackle soaring costs.               
